name: Sarah Jenkins
title: Senior Luxury Estate Agent
bio: As an agent who's an expert in this local area, I bring a wealth of knowledge and expertise about buying and selling real estate here. It's not the same everywhere, so you need someone you can trust for up-to-date information. I am eager to serve you.

name: Michael Chang
title: Luxury Condo Specialist
bio: Michael Chang has over 10 years of experience in the Miami luxury condo market. Specializing in high-end penthouses and waterfront properties, Michael is dedicated to finding the perfect view for his clients.

name: Elena Rodriguez
title: Waterfront Specialist
bio: Elena Rodriguez brings a passion for coastal living to every transaction. With a focus on exclusive waterfront estates, she helps clients find their dream paradise in Miami's most sought-after neighborhoods.

name: James Wilson
title: Commercial Real Estate Expert
bio: James Wilson is your go-to expert for commercial investments. From office spaces to retail locations, James has the market insight and negotiation skills to maximize your ROI.

name: Linda Parker
title: Investment Portfolio Manager
bio: Linda specialize in helping investors build and manage profitable real estate portfolios. Her data-driven approach ensures you make the smartest investment decisions.

name: Robert Chen
title: Penthouse Specialist
bio: Robert Chen is dedicated to the ultra-luxury market. He focuses exclusively on penthouse and sky-home properties, offering discreet and professional service to elite clientele.
